      *
      **** get the date/time stamp of the apics/pt scan
     C                     EXSR GETTM
     C                     MOVE @@TIME    TIME3  160
      *
      **** calculate the elapsed time between scan 2 and scan 3.
     C           TIME3     SUB  TIME2     TMDIFF 160
      *
      **** if barcode from screen 3 is the same as the barcode from screen 2.
      ***  and the elapsed time is less than 2 seconds, then it was a miss scan
      ***  due to the trigger on the scanner itself....<known hardware issue>..
      ***  so, just clear and redisplay screen 3.
      *******    SAVBC3    IFEQ SAVBC2
      *******    TMDIFF    ANDLT2000
      *******              CLEARDSP03
      *******              GOTO #SCRN3
      *******              ENDIF
